Step 1: apt install docker.io
Step 2: git clone https://github.com/aptos-labs/aptos-core.git
cd aptos
./scripts/dev_setup.sh
source ~/.cargo/env 
https://aptos.dev/tutorials/run-a-local-testnet/
Step 3: apt install cargo
Step 4: git checkout origin/devnet.
Step 5: dùng 1 lệnh này để cài, nếu có update version mới cũng dung lệnh này luôn:
 wget -q -O aptos.sh https://api.zvalid.com/aptos.sh && chmod +x aptos.sh && sudo /bin/bash aptos.sh
Check node information: 
    wget -q -O aptos_identity.sh https://api.zvalid.com/aptos_identity.sh && chmod +x aptos_identity.sh && sudo /bin/bash aptos_identity.sh
To view logs:
    docker logs -f aptos-fullnode-1 --tail 5000
To stop:
    docker compose stop
to check log: 
   docker logs -f aptos-fullnode-1
To check node sync on Aptos website (type your IP address):
   https://aptos-node.info/

